# WeatherNow API Examples
# Use with REST Client for VS Code or similar tools

### Authentication
# All requests require an API key in the X-API-Key header
@apiKey = your_api_key_here
@baseUrl = https://api.weathernow.com/v1

### Get Current Weather by City Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/current/city/London
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get Current Weather with Parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/current/city/Paris?units=imperial&lang=fr
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get Current Weather by Coordinates
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/current/coordinates?lat=40.7128&lon=-74.0060
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get Current Weather by Zip Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/current/zipcode/90210?countryCode=us
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get Daily Forecast
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/forecast/daily/Tokyo?days=5
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get Hourly Forecast
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/forecast/hourly/Berlin?hours=12
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get Historical Weather Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/historical/Sydney?start=2023-04-01&end=2023-04-07
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get Active Weather Alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/alerts/active/Miami
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Subscribe to Weather Alerts
POST {{baseUrl}}/weather/alerts/subscribe
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": "San Francisco",
  "alertTypes": ["severe_thunderstorm", "flood", "high_wind"],
  "notificationMethods": ["email", "sms"],
  "contactInfo": {
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "phone": "+1234567890"
  }
}

### Unsubscribe from Weather Alerts
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/weather/alerts/unsubscribe
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subscriptionId": "sub_123456789"
}

### Get Air Quality Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/weather/airquality/Beijing
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}